Name: Alephant
About the game: Aleph is the first letter of the Hebrew alphabet, and it is generally silent . However, it can be combined with the niqqud (vowels) to make a sound . A word-less game about language. Discover and understand apparently arbitrary rules. Find new sounds with unique uses. Talk.
